Enum KandyReducedCallTerminationReason

    public enum KandyReducedCallTerminationReason
extends java.lang.Enum<KandyReducedCallTerminationReason>
    Reduced call termination reason.

    This exists cause the UI needs to show different message / screen to each reason.

    The full call termination reasons are mapped to this enum
